{"word":"αὔλιον","slug":"αὔλιον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>αὔλιον</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:αὐλή'><el>αὐλή</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a country house, cottage</i>, <b>Hhymn.</b>: <i>a fold, stable</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a chamber, cave, grotto</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}